HiyatCab Operations Platform - Build Complete (v2 - Updated)

Branding: HiyatCab (not HiyatCab Ops)
Logo: Custom inline SVG taxi cab logo with Heritage Dark theme colors

Files modified:
- app/globals.css: Heritage Dark theme applied (both :root and .dark blocks)
- app/layout.tsx: Updated metadata title/description, added dark class to html
- app/page.tsx: Complete HiyatCab Operations Platform with 5 tabs, custom logo, production-ready

Features implemented:
1. Dashboard (Ops Intelligence Agent) - stat cards, query input with history, structured response display, copy-to-clipboard
2. Support Triage - issue form with user type/category selectors, severity badges, editable drafted response, internal actions checklist
3. Pricing & Surge Analysis - city/zone/date filters, ride type pills, peak periods table, recommendation cards with impact badges
4. Compliance Review - full driver form, verdict badge, validation checklist with pass/fail icons, flags, expiry alerts, reasoning
5. Reports & Scheduling - report type pills, email delivery via Gmail, schedule management with activate/pause toggle, execution logs

Infrastructure:
- parseLLMJson from @/lib/jsonParser for bulletproof JSON parsing
- callAIAgent from @/lib/aiAgent for all agent calls
- Scheduler integration (listSchedules, pauseSchedule, resumeSchedule, updateScheduleMessage, cronToHuman, getScheduleLogs)
- useCopyToClipboard from @/lib/clipboard
- react-icons/hi2 and react-icons/fi for all icons (no lucide-react)
- PageErrorBoundary wrapping all content
- Agent status panel in sidebar showing active agent
- Responsive: mobile sidebar with overlay, desktop sidebar toggle
- Loading skeletons, error states, empty states, inline status messages
- Heritage Dark theme consistently applied
- No toast/sonner, no OAuth flows, no emojis
